
sample_ecies: Verify ECIES Encrypt and Decrypt modes of operation
              for input data in the container sample

Input required for ECIES operation:
- Plain Data to be encrypted
- Key

Ouput:
- Cipher Data

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_ecies.img

To send data to container:
$ cmtest data -f100 'Run tests'

Note: On receiving data from HLOS, ECIES Encrypt and Decrypt modes of
operation are verified.

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
